goal:
Established in 1998, Quantlab is a leading developer of quantitative trading strategies that are deployed in more than 40 markets around the world.

Quantlab believes that fair, efficient and competitive public markets best serve investors and promotes these principles through its education efforts.
interests: Competition, Economic and Financial Affairs, Financial Stability, Financial Services and Capital Markets Union , Internal Market, Taxation
